        "subheading": "<p><strong>Materials</strong></p>",
        "title": "<p>A Foundation in Form & Tone</p>",
        "description": "<p>The metal you choose forms the foundation of your jewellery - shaping not only its aesthetic, but how it wears, ages, and becomes part of your everyday.</p><p><br/>Each metal carries its own tone, character and set of properties. From the warmth of yellow gold to the softness of silver, these materials are chosen not only for how they look, but for how they feel over time.</p>",
        "feature_text": "<p>At Natalie Marie Jewellery, we approach metals with the same intention as our stones - prioritising quality, longevity and responsible sourcing.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
