        "title": "<p>Our Approach</p>",
        "description": "<p>We work with a considered combination of new and recycled materials, depending on the design and performance required.</p><p>At Natalie Marie Jewellery, we prioritise the use of certified Australian gold wherever possible across our online collections, bespoke creations, and One of a Kind pieces.</p><p>We partner with accredited suppliers who align with our due diligence framework. <br/></p><p>We prioritise traceability and transparency wherever possible. </p><p>We recycle all studio scrap and excess materials through accredited refineries.<br/>We continue to evolve our sourcing practices as part of our ongoing sustainability journey. </p><p>Each metal is alloyed to ensure durability, wearability, and longevity to ensure it will be treasured for generations.<br/></p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
