        "title": "<p><em>Rose Gold</em></p>",
        "description": "<p>Soft, Romantic & Distinctive</p><p>Rose gold is created by alloying gold with copper, giving it its signature blush tone.<br/></p><ul><li>Warm, pink undertone</li><li>Subtle yet distinctive</li><li>Complements a wide range of skin tones</li></ul><p>Rose gold offers a softer interpretation of gold - romantic, modern, and quietly expressive.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
