        "subheading": "",
        "title": "<p><em>White Gold</em></p>",
        "description": "<p>Refined & Contemporary<br/>White gold is created by alloying gold with white metals such as palladium or silver, resulting in a cooler-toned finish.<br/>It is typically coated with rhodium plating to enhance its brightness.<br/></p><ul><li>Cool, silvery appearance</li><li>Polished and luminous</li><li>May require re-plating over time to maintain its finish</li></ul><p>White gold feels clean, modern and refined, offering a contemporary alternative to traditional gold tones.</p>",
        "colour_style": "dark",
        "button_1_text": "",
        "button_1_link": "",
        "button_style": "underline"
      }
    },
